Modifications made in this fork

This fork was created from the Home Assistant ONVIF integration as
shipped in Home Assistant Core version 2026.7.2. The following files
were modified to add support for H.265 (HEVC) and H.265+ profiles:

  - device.py
      * async_get_profiles() extended to accept H.264, H.265 and
        H.265+ media profiles instead of filtering out anything
        that is not H.264.
      * Max-resolution calculation extended to consider H.265 and
        H.265+ profiles alongside H.264.

  - config_flow.py
      * Profile validation during the setup flow extended to accept
        H.264, H.265 and H.265+ profiles.

All other files and functionality (PTZ, events, imaging, snapshots,
and the remainder of the integration) are unmodified from the
original Home Assistant ONVIF integration and remain subject to the
Apache License, Version 2.0 referenced above.

